text: Herznach was a municipality of the district of Laufenburg in the canton of Aargau in Switzerland. On 1 January 2023, the former municipalities of Herznach and Ueken merged to form the new municipality of Herznach-Ueken. == References == == Other websites == * Official website of the municipality of Herznach Category:Former municipalities of Aargau
